  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Kushagra Dixit\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                    <a>Kushagra Dixit</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/87654367/TNN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TNN</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On May 28, 2026 at 05:45 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                            <li>\n                                                        \n                                                            \n                                                                Read by \n                                                            \n                                                            100 Professionals\n                                                        \n                                                    </li>\n                                                                                    </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p><a href=\"/tag/new+delhi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">New Delhi</a>: Lok Nayak Jai Prakash Narayan Hospital has become the country’s first 2,000-bedded govt hospital to receive the <a href=\"/tag/national+quality+assurance+standards+%28nqas%29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">National Quality Assurance Standards (NQAS)</a> certification from <a href=\"/tag/union+health+ministry\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Union health ministry</a>, officials informed on Monday.The certification recognises Delhi govt-run tertiary care hospital’s performance across critical healthcare quality indicators, including <a href=\"/tag/patient+safety\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">patient safety</a>, <a href=\"/tag/infection+control\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">infection control</a>, clinical services and hospital administration.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>Praising the hospital staff, medical director <a href=\"/tag/dr+b+l+chaudhary\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Dr B L Chaudhary</a> described the achievement as a result of “collective dedication, teamwork and commitment” shown by doctors, nurses, faculty members, sanitation workers, security personnel, PWD staff and administrative employees.</p>\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>According to hospital authorities, LNJP Hospital secured exceptionally high scores in the NQAS assessment. It achieved 99.4% in service provision, 96.1% in patient rights, 97.6% in clinical services, 97% in infection control and 95.6% in <a href=\"/tag/quality+management\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">quality management</a>. The hospital also scored 99.5% in patient privacy and dignity, while recording a patient satisfaction score of 87.3%.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>Among specialised facilities, the pharmacy department scored 95.8%, the ICU 96.7% and the haemodialysis centre 97.9%.Officials said the certification follows years of systemic reforms and infrastructure strengthening undertaken at the hospital. Measures included implementation of strict infection-control practices, scientific sanitisation systems, biomedical waste management protocols and mandatory infection-prevention training for healthcare workers.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>The hospital also introduced digital monitoring and patient feedback systems, transparent grievance redressal mechanisms, improved drug inventory management, uninterrupted electricity and water supply systems, patient-centric administrative reforms and standardised treatment protocols.Hospital authorities said the NQAS accreditation will also bring financial benefits. Under <a href=\"/tag/ayushman+bharat-pradhan+mantri+jan+arogya+yojana+%28ab-pmjay%29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Ayushman Bharat-Pradhan Mantri Jan Arogya Yojana (AB-PMJAY)</a>, NQAS-certified hospitals are eligible for an additional 15% incentive over standard package rates. LNJP Hospital is expected to receive over Rs 2 crore annually as an additional financial incentive.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>Officials said the certification reinforces public trust in govt healthcare institutions and demonstrates that high-quality, patient-centric healthcare delivery is achievable within India’s public health system.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Kushagra Dixit</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Kushagra Dixit</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/87654367/TNN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TNN</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On May 28, 2026 at 05:45 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On May 28, 2026 at 05:45 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">2 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                                        <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figure> -->\n        \n            \n                \n                    <h2>All about ETHealthworld industry right on your smartphone! </h2>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download the ETHealthworld App</a> and get the Realtime updates and Save your favourite articles.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                                            <!-- <div class=\"app-store-container desktop-view\">\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"\" aria-label=\"Play Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-g-play.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"App Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-app-store.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                        </div>   